dct_title_s: Goa, fortissima Indiæ vrbs in Christianorum potestatem, anno salutis 1509 deuenit
dct_description_sm: Pictorial view of Goa, India. German text on verso; p. 58. From: Beschreibung und Contrafactur der Vornembster Stät der Welt / Georgius Braun und Franciscus Hohenberg. Zu Cölln : [T. Graminaeus ... et al.], 1572-1618. Historic Maps originally issued on sheet with 3 other views.
